    <fr:title text="Exposed">Exposed</fr:title>
    <fr:authors />
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>Characters who are caught with their guard down or otherwise defenceless are Exposed and act as if they have 0<fr:link type="local" href="guard.xml" addr="guard" title="Guard">GD</fr:link>.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>If they remedy their situation then they are no longer Exposed. Traps and ambushes typically catch victims Exposed.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
