            <fr:addr type="user">virtues</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>virtues.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Virtues">Virtues</fr:title>
            <fr:authors />
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>There are three virtues for knights: VIGOUR, CLARITY, SPIRIT.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>They roll d12 + d6 for each of them and keep the results.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>
              <fr:ul><fr:li>Vigour is restored by consuming Sustenance or spending a full day in warm hospitality.</fr:li>
    <fr:li>Clarity is restored by consuming Stimulant or receiving guidance from a Seer.</fr:li>
    <fr:li>Spirit is restored by consuming Sacrament or indulging a Passion.</fr:li></fr:ul>
            </fr:p>
            <fr:p>At VIG 0 you are Exhausted and cannot Attack if you have moved this turn.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>At CLA 0 you are <fr:link type="local" href="exposed.xml" addr="exposed" title="Exposed">Exposed</fr:link>.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>At SPI 0 your attacks are <fr:link type="local" href="impaired.xml" addr="impaired" title="Impaired">Impaired</fr:link>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
          <fr:backmatter />
        </fr:tree>
      </fr:mainmatter>
      <fr:backmatter />
    </fr:tree>
